\c 25
\s Bhiridhadhi anorumbidza ukuru hwaMwari
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Bhiridhadhi muShuhi akapindura, akati:
\v 2 Umambo nokutyisa zvinaye; iye unoyananisa pamatunhu ake akakwirira.
\v 3 Hondo dzake dzingaverengwa here? Ndianiko asingavhenekerwi nechiedza chake?
\v 4 Zvino munhu angava akarurama sei pamberi paMwari? Nomunhu akazvarwa nomukadzi angava akachena sei?
\v 5 Tarira, nomwedziwo unoshaiwa kubhinya, nenyeredzi hadzizakachena kwazvo pamberi pake.
\v 6 Ndoda munhu, iro gonye! Nomwanakomana womunhu, iro gonye!
